          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-6356 target: all bulk IO must be (un)wrapped if necessary",
        "message": "LU-6356 target: all bulk IO must be (un)wrapped if necessary\n\nIn target_bulk_io() ensure all types of bulk IOs are processed through\nsptlrpc_svc_wrap_bulk() and sptlrpc_svc_unwrap_bulk().\nOtherwise data that is supposed to be sent encrypted is not, which\nleads to malfunction on the other side.\nOther error is to receive encrypted data and try to process it without\ndecrypting it first.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sebastien.buisson@bull.net>\nChange-Id: I12200f1cbf8db7318ead49367dbc9b9327223289\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
